item.title: brute forcing American Tourister lock
item.description:
00:24 Wednesday 20 January 2016 JST Lin got a new suitcase!
I rotated one number on the lock while pressing the combination reset, and now I cannot unlock the lock. Fuck fuck fuck. Lin just bought this suitcase today and asked if I can set the combination to something other than 000. Done. 01:24 I have rolled through all the combinations with 2 zeroes, and I’ve gone through the first 110 or so consecutive combinations.
